+# Step-009 Endpoint Gate Is Cleared On The Frozen Far-Field Ledger
+
+Status: `VERIFIED` with `INFERRED` branch verdict
+
+Explorations 001 through 003 now freeze the full Step-009 endpoint gate on one
+inherited far-field ledger:
+
+- one theorem package and contradiction line on the suitable-weak /
+  Leray-Hopf plus LEI floor;
+- one live endpoint object, the complete pairing `I_p^far`;
+- one cash-out shape and gain currency, namely a smaller effective coefficient
+  on that same full pairing;
+- one minimum threshold, positive-margin net shrinkage after later debt;
+- and two admission rules, the same-scale immediate-failure rule and the Tao
+  screen that is only meaningful when it returns as coefficient shrinkage on
+  the full pairing.
+
+The Step-009 verdict is therefore:
+`endpoint frozen, proceed to prior-art and packaging screening`.
+
+This survival is narrow. Later steps may still compare mechanism families,
+tensor packages, comparators, and reconstruction bookkeeping, but they may not
+renegotiate the frozen endpoint, replace the full pairing with a surrogate, or
+treat Tao sensitivity as a substitute for endpoint-level gain. No tensor
+package is admitted yet.
+
